about_product: [UNIQUE 6 PCS CAT TOYS]: Our cat feather wand set includes 4 adorable insect-themed replacement lures (grasshopper, bee, cicada, and longhorn beetle) and 2 durable wands. Each bug toy flutters and jumps like real prey, activating your cat’s natural chase and pounce instincts. Feather-tipped surprises add extra excitement! A truly fun and unique offering on Amazon

[HIGH-QUALITY AND SAFE MATERIAL]: All cat teaser wands and accessories are handmade from safe, non-toxic materials. The sturdy wand features a flexible toy head for enhanced durability and playfulness. This set also includes an extra pack of bells for added fun. ⚠ PLEASE NEVER LEAVE YOUR CAT UNATTENDED WITH THESE TOYS TO AVOID RISK OF CHOKING

[CUTE BUG TOY REPLACEMENT]: This teaser toy comes with a variety of bug-themed feather lures that are easily replaceable—simply screw the toy attachment into the nut on top of the wand. When fully assembled with the spring attachment, the total length reaches approximately 23.6 inches, providing ample range for dynamic play and interactive fun

[KEEP YOUR CAT HEALTHY AND ACTIVE]: These cute and realistic bugs will drive your cat wild! The interactive design stimulates natural hunting instincts, encouraging flipping, jumping, chasing, and hunting. Great for exercise, improving agility, strengthening immunity, and reducing obesity and anxiety

[PLAY WITH YOUR CAT]: Just a slight wave of the wand instantly grabs your cat’s attention and draws them closer. Its ideal length encourages cats to play around you, strengthening your bond. Reward good play with timely pets and affection. Playing with your kitten has never been so relaxing and joyful!
